"He ha haaaa" Wildrider roars in laughter. He sees the base coming up.
"Ohhhh, Im gonna beat... you" He tries to taunt, but he comes to a dead
stop. The oil leaking out of him left a wide trail, he was running on
empty.

Speedbreaker pulls up behind him. "Wildrider, you oaf, you really should
keep better care of yourself". "Shudap" Wildrider snaps. Speebreaker
tranforms, and wheels him the rest of the way to base. He then walks in,
and goes for a cube.


Beastbox walks up to Skullgrin, "This sucks, Why do we have to stay here?".
He looks back at the prisoners.
